UNITED STATES of America v. BOARD OF COUNTY COMMISSIONERS OF PAWNEE COUNTY, OKLAHOMA. No. 1690. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. April 11, 1938. Chester A. Brewer, Asst. U. S. Atty., of Tulsa, Okl. Horace Ballaine, County Atty., of Pawnee, Okl., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS, BRATTON, and WILLIAMS, Circuit Judges.

PEB CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on motion of appellant.
